  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要做一个甘特图来对比两种任务结束方式的差异，一个是按天数算，一个是手动指定具体日期。标题就叫「Exclusive end dates」吧，副标题说明一下「Manual date should end on 3d」。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "gantt"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那日期格式我们统一用YYYY-MM-DD，坐标轴只显示天数可以吗？这样对比起来更直观。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat",
        "axisFormat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，axisFormat用%d就行。然后第一个section叫Section1，里面放两个任务。第一个任务「2 Days」从2019-01-01开始，持续2天。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "Section1",
        "2 Days",
        "2d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一个任务我标记为ID 1，2019-01-01开始，2d结束。那第二个任务「Manual Date」呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "2 Days",
        "1",
        "2019-01-01",
        "2d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二个任务同样从2019-01-01开始，但结束日期手动指定到2019-01-03，这样虽然也是3天跨度，但用的是显式日期而不是duration。标记为ID 2。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Manual Date",
        "2",
        "2019-01-01",
        "2019-01-03"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经画好了。两个任务时间范围看起来一样，但一个用2d一个用2019-01-03作为结束，确实能体现exclusive end dates的区别。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Manual Date",
        "2d",
        "2019-01-03"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，我刚才说错了——Manual Date的结束日期应该是2019-01-03，但这样实际上是3天（1号、2号、3号），和2d的2天不对等。不过这正是我们想展示的：手动指定2019-01-03时，甘特图会包含到3号当天结束，而2d则是从1号开始算两天到2号结束。让我确认一下，Manual Date确实要写到2019-01-03对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Manual Date",
        "2019-01-03",
        "2d",
        "3d"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误。现在图里「2 Days」显示到1月2日，「Manual Date」显示到1月3日，标题也注明了Manual date should end on 3d，对比效果很清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "2 Days",
        "Manual Date",
        "title",
        "3d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
